The People of the State of Illinois, Plaintiff-Appellee, v. Roger L. Knell, Defendant-Appellant.(No. 72-206;Second DistrictSeptember 19, 1974.Ralph Ruebner and Adam Lutynski, both State Appellate Defender’s Office, of Elgin, for appellant.Philip G. Reinhard, State’s Attorney, of Rockford (James W. Jerz and Edward Morris, both of Model District State’s Attorneys Office, of counsel), for the People.
